<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT-Intl Gaming covered again by Everen.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT-Intl Gaming covered again by Everen.</headline>
<text>
<p>--EVEREN Securities Inc said Tuesday it reinstated coverage of International Gaming Technology with investment ratings of market performer for the intermediate term and outperformer for the long term.</p>
<p>--Its earnings estimates for the manufacturer of gaming machines are $1.07 for FY97 and $1.20 for FY98.</p>
<p>--International Gaming was trading at 18-1/2, off 1/2.</p>
<p>	     ((Chicago newsdesk 312 408-8787))</p>
